properties.text: Press mouse button or 'Q' to start this SHIP !
To finish level you must fly through all yellow circles.
If you want atleast 2 stars you must fly through all orange circles.
To get 3rd start you must be quick.
You can zoom in and out using scroll.
If you missed a checkpoint you can restart game by pressing 'X'.
To fire a space rope press 'W'.
You can fire up to 2 ropes.
This is a broken ship. Your duty is to help it. Transport this ship into dock area.
You can fire up to 2 ropes, this stops object from rotating.
Find broken ship and save it. Tip of the day: follow the arrows.
Hurry up ! The ship is in danger !
